All content, code comments, documentation, commit messages, variable names, and explanations should be written in **English**.

- Do not use French or any other language.
- All AI responses must be written in English, including:
  - Generated docblocks and function/method comments
  - Example content for placeholder text
  - Explanations or justifications for decisions
- If the input is in French, convert it automatically to English when responding.
